config ZMK_I2C_SCANNER
	bool "Boot-time I2C bus scanner (diagnostic)"
	depends on I2C
	help
	  Probes I2C addresses 0x08-0x77 on i2c0 and logs which ACK. Diagnostic only.

config ZMK_GPIO_FINDER
	bool "Boot-time GPIO INT-finder (diagnostic)"
	help
	  Watches free nice!nano GPIO pads and logs which goes LOW. Diagnostic only.

config ZMK_PIM447_POLL
	bool "Pimoroni PIM447 trackball (polled input driver)"
	depends on I2C && INPUT
	help
	  Polling I2C driver for the PIM447 trackball. Binds to the t0bybr module's
	  "zmk,pimoroni-pim447" devicetree binding but reads on a timer instead of
	  using the interrupt line. Reports movement + click via the input subsystem.
	  INPUT is already provided by ZMK_POINTING; depend on it (do NOT select, or
	  it forms a Kconfig dependency loop through I2C).
